==English==
[[Image:JapanSumoMatch.jpg|thumbnail|Sumo Match]]
===Etymology===
{{Ja.}} ''to mutually rush at''
===Pronunciation===
*[[w:AHD|AHD]]: soo͞'mō
*[[w:IPA|IPA]]: /ˈsuːməʊ/
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /"su:m@U/

===Noun===
'''sumo'''
#{{sumo}} a [[stylised]] [[Japanese]] form of [[wrestling]] in which a [[wrestler]] loses if he is [[forced]] from the ring, or if any part of his body except the [[sole]]s of his [[feet]] touch the [[ground]].

